EmailTemplate.name: ICD - Follow-up Email ( 2.x PV Sup )
EmailTemplate.subject: SunPower Internet Communication Down - {!Case.Contact}
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hi {!Contact.FirstName},
Thank you for choosing SunPower as your solar provider.
We noticed that your SunPower Monitoring System has not been reporting energy production information to our server. For your convenience I have attached basic troubleshooting steps to help you address common issues.
To get troubleshooting assistance if you are at home, please call us at 1-877-344-6637.We're here for you Monday through Friday from 7 a.m. until 4 p.m.
Please note that case will be closed if we do not receive a response via call or email in 5 business days.
Regards,
New Homes Customer Support | Tel: 1-877-344-6637 residential.service@sunpowercorp.com
